:

*Stoga* je vreme da svi učestvujemo u ovom procesu. (Therefore, it is time for us all to participate in this process.)

*Stoga* se često pribegava zaštitnim merama. (Therefore, protective measures are often resorted to.)

*Stoga* smo morali da promenimo plan. (So we had to change the plan.)

*Stoga* je bitno da svi budemo svesni toga. (Therefore, it is important that we all be aware of this.)

*Stoga* su mnogi ljudi ušli u paniku. (So many people panicked.)